With Recycle!, you always have the collection calendar at hand! This useful app provides easy access to collection times, sorting information and collection points directly on your smartphone. Having doubts about sorting? Or wondering if your plastic packaging belongs in the PMD bag? Recycle! has all the answers you need.

Features:

- Notifications: Receive collection reminders at self-selected times and never forget to put your waste out in time for collection!
- Calendar: The calendar gives you a monthly overview of upcoming collection times, as well as the opening hours of recycling parks in your area.
- Collection points: Quickly find collection points for batteries, electronics, glass, and more in your area. Check opening hours and closing days.
- Sorting guide: Do you have questions about sorting waste? Consult our sorting guide for clear answers and useful tips to recycle better.

Recycle! is a joint initiative of Bebat and Fost Plus, with the support of local waste intermunicipalities. Together we strive for a cleaner future for our planet.

- Quick detection: translations begin as you type

Why use multiple apps when you can track all your TCGs in one place? Most collectors collect multiple TCGs. Whether you are a Pokemon collector, Magic collector, YuGiOh collector, MetaZoo collector, or even a Funko collector, this app is for you!



Collectr is a next-generation portfolio manager. We allow you to manage, track and value all your raw, graded and sealed cards in the palm of your hand. It’s never been easier to view your TCG collections as a portfolio.

KEY FEATURES

Get God’s Word for free on your devices with the Bible App by YouVersion. Connect with God through Scripture by reading, listening, Plans, Daily Refresh, Verse of the Day, and so much more!

Choose from 1,750+ languages and 2,500+ Bible versions. Make it your Bible by adding Friends, choosing Plans, creating Verse Images, highlighting, and making notes.

Bring your friends with you and explore the Bible together. Have honest conversations about Scripture. Grow together and share what you discover.

People are reading, listening to, watching, and sharing the free Bible App by YouVersion on over 500 million devices worldwide. Join the global Community today! Download the Bible App.


EXPLORE GOD’S WORD
* Choose from thousands of Bible versions in over 1,750 languages
* Pick from over 60 languages for your Bible App interface
* Download select Bible versions to access when you’re offline
* Listen to select Bible versions and enjoy skip, playback speed, and timer controls.
* Learn more about the Verse of the Day in Guided Scripture with an engaging video and personal reflection questions

* Choose from thousands of Plans that focus on specific topics, portions of Scripture, or the entire Bible in a year
* Watch videos from Christian organizations such as Bible Project and The Chosen
* Search for what the Bible says about any topic you’re wondering about
* Tap on a verse to see your Notes and related content such as videos, Plans, and study notes

MAKE IT YOUR BIBLE
* Themes let you select a color palette for your entire Bible App experience
* Create and download Verse Images for any verse you’d like—it’s shareable art
* Highlight with custom colors and create notes
* Bookmark passages to share, memorize, and keep at the front of your mind
* Share verses with friends using social media, email, or text
* Add notes on any verse—make them private or let your Friends see them
* Access your account from any supported device
* Adjust lighting, font, font size, and line spacing for easy reading

BRING YOUR FRIENDS ALONG
* Center your friendships around Scripture by adding your Friends to the Bible App
* See an activity feed that shows what you and your Friends are noting, bookmarking, and highlighting
* Comment on the Verse of the Day with your Friends—ask questions and share how God is speaking to you
* Write your own prayers and share them with your Friends to pray together
* Do Plans together and discuss what you’re learning

CONNECT WITH YOUVERSION
* Contact Support from inside the Bible App
* Join the @youversion Community on Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, TikTok & Pinterest
* Catch up on the latest at blog.youversion.com
* Access the Bible online at bible.com

Download the world’s #1 Bible App and enjoy the Bible experience loved by millions!

Lightning-fast and accurate coin recognition.

Read street signs in a foreign country, translate manuals of your overseas purchases or the text of any picture you already have in your phone. Bible Path is a thoughtfully designed app aimed at enriching your spiritual journey with scriptures that offer guidance and holy inspiration. Whether you seek daily inspiration, devotional reflections, or a deeper understanding of the scriptures, Bible Path provides a serene and supportive environment for personal growth.

Key Features:

Bible Chat:
Engage in conversations about faith, prayers, and scriptures with Bible Chat. This feature allows you to explore different interpretations of the scripture, ask questions, and connect with a community of fellow seekers in a holy atmosphere. The chat interface makes it easy to share your thoughts on scriptures and devotional topics with others.

Audio Bible:
Immerse yourself in the holy scriptures through our audio Bible. Perfect for quiet moments of reflection or during daily activities, the narrated scriptures help you stay connected to the Word of God. Whether you’re listening to audio prayers or meditating on the scripture, the app makes it easy to integrate devotional practices into your routine.

Inspirational Verses and Prayers:
Receive a daily dose of inspiration with verses and prayers that uplift and guide you. Each scripture verse and prayer is carefully chosen to offer spiritual nourishment, guiding you in your devotional journey with the holy scriptures.

Personalized Daily Reflections:
Reflect on personalized insights based on the holy scriptures and prayers that resonate with your spiritual needs. These reflections are crafted to help you ponder biblical themes and integrate their teachings into your daily life through consistent devotional practices.

Interactive Bible Studies:
Deepen your understanding of the Bible with our interactive study guides. These resources provide comprehensive insights and context, suitable for both personal study and group discussion, focusing on the holy scriptures to enrich your devotional life.

Faith Building Exercises and Prayers:
Engage in exercises designed to strengthen your faith and understanding, complemented by powerful prayers. These activities encourage you to reflect on scriptures and apply them to your life, guiding you in devotional practices.

Studies and Resources:
Access a wide range of study materials and resources tailored to different levels of biblical knowledge. Whether you are just beginning your journey or seeking advanced understanding of the scriptures, Bible Path provides a supportive resource filled with devotional insights and reflections on the holy scriptures.

Why Choose Bible Path?
Bible Path is a spiritual companion, offering a calm and nurturing space for exploring the scriptures and growing in faith. With tools like chat, audio resources, and study guides, the app is designed to be a gentle guide, helping you find clarity, comfort, and deeper meaning in your spiritual journey.

Download Bible Path and begin a journey of reflection, learning, and spiritual growth. Let this app be a quiet support in your daily life, offering holy guidance and wisdom from the scriptures through prayers, verses, and more.

Explore your roots, find new relatives, and make amazing discoveries with genealogical search tools and an intuitive family tree builder. Join our global community of users to map your ancestors and family history effortlessly.

LiveMemory™
Make your memories come to life as AI-powered videos with LiveMemory™! Turn photos into video clips with AI-powered photo animation and relive your favorite moments. Animate entire family photos and see your memories reimagined in lifelike videos. Our AI video generator creates animated memories that bring photos to life. Share on social media and amaze your family and friends!

Build Your Family Tree
Start your family tree by entering a few names, and MyHeritage will do the rest. Our matching technologies for genealogical research will automatically find new information for you in our diverse collection of 81 million family trees built by users all over the world, and in our huge database of 21 billion historical records. Watch your family history come to life and make fascinating discoveries with this family tree maker app.

Make Instant Family History Discoveries
MyHeritage’s genealogical search features can easily match your family tree to other family trees and historical records to provide you with meaningful new insights about your ancestors. Enrich your family tree with MyHeritage’s powerful search and matching technologies:

Smart Matches™
A unique technology that automatically matches your family tree to other family trees, revealing new information about your family origins.
Record Matches: an innovative technology that finds new information about your ancestors in our global collection of historical records.
Instant Discoveries™: a useful feature that adds entire branches and photos to your family tree in one click.

Find Your Ancestors in Historical Records
Explore your family history in MyHeritage’s vast database of more than 33 billion historical records from around the world. The historical record collections include vital records (birth, marriage, and death certificates) from 66 countries; census and immigration records; gravestone and burial records; and much more.

MyHeritage DNA
Locked inside your DNA is your unique ethnic makeup. The test consists of a simple cheek swab and reveals your genetic heritage across 2,114 geographic regions — more than any other test. It also matches you to relatives you never knew existed in our DNA database of 9 million people. View your DNA results on the app; they’re private and secure, and will never be shared or sold.

Deep Nostalgia™
Have you ever dreamed of bringing historical family photos to life? With MyHeritage’s Deep Nostalgia™ feature, your historical family photos will come to life and you’ll see your ancestors’ faces move! Deep Nostalgia™ uses AI technology to breathe new life into historical photos and recreate moments from your family history. Pull out those photo albums and discover your ancestry as you connect to cherished family memories and trace history across generations.

Enrich Your Family Tree with Photos
Capture and share your family memories, old and new. Scan your family photos directly from the app and use our AI-based photo tools to bring your family history to life. Repair scratched or damaged photos with Photo Repair, colorize your black and white photos, and bring blurry faces into focus with the MyHeritage Photo Enhancer. Record the stories behind your family photos with the Photo Storyteller™ and preserve them for generations to come.

Download MyHeritage today to uncover your roots with an all-in-one family tree app, photo animator, and ancestry search tool.

Discover the True Value of Your Vinyl — Instantly
What if that dusty record in your garage is worth hundreds—or even thousands? VinylSnap makes it easy to find out. With one quick photo, instantly identify your vinyl, get a reliable market price, see grading suggestions, and save it to your collection.
VinylSnap is your go-to vinyl companion, perfect for collectors, resellers, or anyone who just found a box of old LPs in the attic. Try it free and see what your records are really worth!
What Can VinylSnap Do?
- Reliable Market Valuation  
  Get a trusted reference price before you buy, sell, or store—know if you’ve found a $10 album or a $1,000 treasure.
- Instant Identification with Rich Details  
  Scan the label to unlock pressing info, release year, tracklist, and artist stories—works with most 12", 10", and 7" records.
- Grading Suggestions  
  Helpful VG / VG+ / NM guidance based on visible wear, label clarity, and jacket condition—so you can price and sell with confidence.
- Your Digital Vinyl Shelf  
  Save every record you scan and track your collection’s total value over time—see how your vinyl library grows in worth.
- Learn & Explore  
  Read exclusive articles on record-breaking vinyl sales, collector tips, and essential guides for anyone new to vinyl—so you know what to look for and how to protect it.
Who Is VinylSnap For?
 • Beginners  
  Just getting into vinyl? VinylSnap helps you understand what you have and how much it’s worth—no experience needed. 
 • Collectors  
  Build a well-organized vinyl archive, track your investments, and make sure your most valuable pressings are properly graded. 
 • Resellers  
  Use VinylSnap to make fast, informed decisions while crate-digging. Know what to buy, what to list, and what to keep.
Why Choose VinylSnap? 
Accurate — Trusted valuation and grading in seconds  
Effortless — Just scan the label, no manual searching  
Insightful — Background knowledge at your fingertips  
Organized — Manage your entire vinyl library in one clean app
Start Scanning with VinylSnap Today! Download now and discover the value behind every record.

Are you a coin collector looking to identify your latest find? Or maybe you stumbled upon a coin and want to know its value? Well, look no further! Introducing the new Coin Identifier - your one-stop-shop for all things coin-related. With just a snap of a picture, our app can identify your coin, provide detailed information about its history, estimate coin value, and even connect you with coin sellers and buyers. No more sifting through endless coin catalogs or scouring the internet for hours. Our app makes coin collecting easy, fun, and profitable. 

Key CoinIn features: 

Identify coins at lightning speed 
You won't have to spend hours searching through reference books or browsing the internet for visual confirmation.

Accurately identify over 270,000 coins 
Our large database contains more than 270 000 coins and allows you to identify any kind of coin. CoinIn scanner takes into account the type of material, time of creation, and coin condition, to provide you with the most precise and reliable information. 

Recognize rare, foreign, and error coins
Whether you're one of the seasoned coin collectors looking for a rare gem, or a newbie who’s just starting out, CoinIn has got you covered. 

Grade coins’ value, track prices in real time
Get an estimation of identified coins’ prices and an idea of the total value of your collection. CoinIn finder uses an API to provide you with a price tracker from numismatics platforms, so you know exactly how much your coins are worth. 

Follow coin collection trends 
Stay up to date with the coin collection series and be the first to add new gold and metal coins to your stock. 

Create a personalized online collection
Record, store, and access your collections right in the app anytime, anywhere. 

With CoinIn, you can turn your coin collection into a treasure trove - get started today!

Translate and learn millions of words and expressions and express yourself as if you were a native speaker.

Reverso is the best tool for those who seek quality translation, looking to master a foreign language: reading, writing or speaking, and it's free.

Students, teachers, business professionals or others, whether beginners or advanced, use Reverso to learn new words or expressions, and eliminate the risk of being mistaken.

It provides you instant translations of the selected text when reading content on your browser, on Safari or any other app.
 
Reverso Context is based on data gathered from millions of real-life texts (official documents, movie subtitles, product descriptions) in both languages. These texts are processed with powerful "big data" algorithms and machine learning to provide you the best results. 

What do we mean by context? The search results (translation) of a specific word or expression are weaved within real-life sentences, so you will be sure to understand and learn exactly how the word can be used, and make no embarrassing mistakes.  

Just type or say the word or expression you wish to translate and the results will appear instantly:  relevant translations, presented with examples of how words are used in sentences.

The app offers flashcards and quizzes based on your search history and favorites to help you memorize them and to improve your language skills. Unlike standard learning tools, it focuses on words and expressions that you really need and want to learn.

Master the articles (lidwoorden) of Dutch nouns. Excel in your Dutch classes and/or impress your native Dutch speaker friends.

SEARCH 
Type the first few characters of a noun and see the article immediately. The app contains a dictionary with more than 73,000 Dutch nouns. Optionally, you can display the translation and definition of the noun.

FAVORITES
To focus on problematic nouns, add them to your Favorites for later reference.

RULES
Although the articles in Dutch language seem quite random, they are not completely so. Learn several handy rules and guidelines for determining the articles.

GAME
Select/guess the articles of nouns presented in random order.
